---
const name = "田中太郎"
const email = "example@example.com"
const pageTitle = `お問い合わせ - ${name}のサイト`
---

<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>{pageTitle}</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="header">
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="/">🏠 ホーム</a>
        <a href="/about">💁 自己紹介</a>
        <a href="/skills">💼 スキル</a>
        <a href="/works">🎨 作品</a>
        <a href="/contact">✉️ お問い合わせ</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="main">
      <h1>お問い合わせ</h1>

      <div class="contact-info">
        <p>お仕事のご依頼・ご相談は、以下の方法でお気軽にご連絡ください。</p>

        <div class="contact-methods">
          <div class="contact-method">
            <h2>✉️ メール</h2>
            <p><a href={`mailto:${email}`}>{email}</a></p>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-method">
            <h2>💬 SNS</h2>
            <p><a href="https://twitter.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">X (Twitter)</a></p>
            <p><a href="https://github.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="form-placeholder">
        <p>📝 お問い合わせフォームは準備中です。</p>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} {name}</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .header {
    background-color: #fff;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
  }

  .nav {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .nav a {
    color: #555;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .nav a:hover {
    color: #4f39fa;
  }

  .main {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #4f39fa;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .contact-info {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .contact-info > p {
    color: #555;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .contact-methods {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .contact-method {
    background-color: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #eee;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .contact-method h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .contact-method a {
    color: #4f39fa;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .contact-method a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .contact-method p {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .form-placeholder {
    background-color: #f8f8f8;
    border: 2px dashed #ddd;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: #888;
  }

  .footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    color: #888;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 600px) {
    .contact-methods {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>